# Git Integration
## Jnkins pipeline - Checkout Git 
you will learn how to **checkout a Git repository** snd list files.

pipeline {
    agent any
    stage {
        stage('Checkout') {
            steps {
                git branch: 'main', url: 'https://github.compathnex/sample-java-app.git'
            }
        }
        stage('List Files') {
            steps {
                sh 'ls-la'
            }
        }
    }
}
 
